(() => { const c = document.createElement('div'); Object.assign(c.style, { position: 'fixed', top: '0', left: '380px', zIndex: '9999', fontFamily: 'Arial, sans-serif', fontSize: '16px', fontWeight: '600', textShadow: '2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4)', background: 'linear-gradient(to right, #00f, #0af)', color: 'transparent', webkitBackgroundClip: 'text' }); const t = document.createElement('span'); t.textContent = 'FPS: '; const v = document.createElement('span'); v.textContent = '0'; c.appendChild(t); c.appendChild(v); document.body.appendChild(c); let f = 0; let n = 0; const u = () => { f = n; n = 0; v.textContent = f; setTimeout(u, 1500); }; u(); const o = () => { n++; requestAnimationFrame(o); }; o(); })();

(()=>{'use strict';const e=document.createElement('style');e.innerHTML='.container{background: linear-gradient(to bottom, red, orange, yellow, green, blue, indigo, violet);box-shadow: 0 0 20px blue, 0 0 40px blue, 0 0 60px blue}';document.head.appendChild(e);})();

(function() {'use strict';var titleLogo = document.getElementById('title-logo');if (titleLogo) {titleLogo.textContent = "Super kanal";titleLogo.style.background = 'linear-gradient(to right, #5bc0de, #0074e4)';titleLogo.style.webkitBackgroundClip = 'text';titleLogo.style.color = 'transparent';titleLogo.style.textShadow = '0 0 10px #0074e4';}})();

document.querySelectorAll('div, span, a, img').forEach(el => el.innerText.toLowerCase().includes('реклама') && (el.style.display = 'none'));

(function(){'use strict';var s=document.getElementById('subtitle-logo');if(s){s.textContent="By Super kanal Visual";s.style.color='red';s.style.textShadow='0 0 10px red';}})();

(function(){'use strict';var e=document.querySelector('.motdtitle');if(e){e.style.display='none';}})();

(function(){'use strict';var e=document.getElementById('motdcontent');if(e){e.style.display='none';}})();

(function() {'use strict';const e='https://www.fonstola.ru/pic/201310/1920x1080/fonstola.ru_128265.jpg';function t() {const t=document.getElementById('lobby-layout');if(t) {t.style.backgroundImage=`url('${e}')`;t.style.backgroundSize='cover';} }t();})();


titleLogo.textContent = "By Super kanal";
titleLogo.style.color = "white";
titleLogo.style.textShadow = "0 0 10px white";
loginButton.style.color = "white";
loginButton.style.textShadow = "0 0 10px white";
loginButton.setAttribute("data-disabled", "false");
var titleLogo = document.getElementById("title-logo");
var loginButton = document.getElementById("login-button");
var clockElement = document.querySelector('.clock');
const imageElement = document.getElementById('yourImageElementId');
imageElement.style.filter = 'blur(40px)';
document.querySelector(".window-ad")?.remove();
